      "content": "but that's the thing... you talk about \"starting over\" or \"filling the space,\" but how do you fill something that's fundamentally broken? it doesn't feel like a house that can be renovated. it feels like the building burned down and all that's left is ash. you can't rebuild a person who doesn't exist anymore. it just feels like a waste of time to keep performing these daily routines for someone who isn't even there.",
